{"tid":2333664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"破壞六四紀念視訊會議 Zoom中國員工遭美起訴","createTime":"2020-12-20T15:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T15:20:22.000Z","uid":284729,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"04f058879486a750074952d92f88be204a2fd9a3","tid":2333664,"uid":284729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"美國檢察官18日起訴總部位於中國的電信企業Zoom雇員金新江(Xinjiang Jin，音譯)。金新江被控在中國政府的要求下，破壞今年5月至6月為紀念六四天安門事件31週年的一連串會議。這些會議使用Zoom的視訊會議系統進行。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2087175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2087175&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=a540977b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2087175</a><br />\n<br />\nUS charges ex-Zoom employee with shutting down Tiananmen Square events <a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-55372493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-55372493&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=4baed877\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-55372493</a>"},{"pid":"29e8d78cce11d40eb1d2fb432323bcad4bbe49af","tid":2333664,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T15:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}